      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "[ComfyUI Туториал](https://docs.comfy.org/tutorials/image/qwen/qwen-image-edit-2511)\n\n\n## Ссылки на модели\n\nВы можете найти модели на [Huggingface Image](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Qwen-Image_ComfyUI/tree/main) или [Huggingface Edit](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Qwen-Image-Edit_ComfyUI/tree/main/split_files/diffusion_models)\n\n**Diffusion model (на выбор)**\n\n- [qwen_image_2512_fp8_e4m3fn.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Qwen-Image_ComfyUI/resolve/main/split_files/diffusion_models/qwen_image_2512_fp8_e4m3fn.safetensors)\n- [qwen_image_2512_bf16.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Qwen-Image_ComfyUI/resolve/main/split_files/diffusion_models/qwen_image_2512_bf16.safetensors)\n\n**GGUF model (Q4, Q8 - на выбор)**\n\n- [unsloth/Qwen-Image-2512-GGUF](https://huggingface.co/unsloth/Qwen-Image-2512-GGUF/tree/main)\n\n**LoRA 2512 (на выбор)**\n\n- [Qwen-Image-2512-Lightning-4steps-V1.0-fp32.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/lightx2v/Qwen-Image-2512-Lightning/resolve/main/Qwen-Image-2512-Lightning-4steps-V1.0-fp32.safetensors)\n- [Qwen-Image-2512-Lightning-8steps-V1.0-fp32.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/lightx2v/Qwen-Image-2512-Lightning/resolve/main/Qwen-Image-2512-Lightning-8steps-V1.0-fp32.safetensors)\n\n**Text encoder (на выбор)** \n\n- [qwen_2.5_vl_7b_fp8_scaled.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Qwen-Image_ComfyUI/resolve/main/split_files/text_encoders/qwen_2.5_vl_7b_fp8_scaled.safetensors)\n- [qwen_2.5_vl_7b.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Qwen-Image_ComfyUI/resolve/main/split_files/text_encoders/qwen_2.5_vl_7b.safetensors)\n\n**VAE**\n\n- [qwen_image_vae.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Qwen-Image_ComfyUI/resolve/main/split_files/vae/qwen_image_vae.safetensors)\n\nModel Storage Location\n\n```\n📂 ComfyUI/\n├── 📂 models/\n│   ├── 📂 diffusion_models/\n│   │      └── qwen_image_2512_fp8_e4m3fn.safetensors\n│   │      └── qwen_image_2512_bf16.safetensors\n│   │      └── qwen-image-2512-Q8_0.gguf     \n│   ├── 📂 loras/\n│   │      └── Qwen-Image-2512-Lightning-4steps-V1.0-fp32.safetensors\n│   │      └── Qwen-Image-2512-Lightning-8steps-V1.0-fp32.safetensors\n│   ├── 📂 text_encoders/\n│   │      └── qwen_2.5_vl_7b_fp8_scaled.safetensors\n│   └── 📂 vae/\n│          └── qwen_image_vae.safetensors\n```\n\n## 🎈 Upscale Model  \n\n### Скачать 4x_NMKD-Siax_200k.pth mode from [ТУТ](https://huggingface.co/uwg/upscaler/resolve/main/ESRGAN/4x_NMKD-Siax_200k.pth?download=true)  \n\n**Положить:** `ComfyUI/models/upscale_models`\n\n\n## 📚 Resources  \n🎥 **Видео по Qwen ComfyUI (плейлист):** [Егор Смышников YT](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLUREBJZfEOoN6ucy5HmKzjyTzi2RkiDF_)  \n\n💬 **Сообщество Гильдия: Генеративный:** [Присоединиться](https://t.me/tribute/app?startapp=sgyZ)"
      ],
      "color": "#000000",
